text: Kangenga is a town in Kenya's Central Province which is about 40 miles (64 kilometers) North-East of Nairobi, the country's capital city. Locations nearby that could be of interest include: Musoma, Moshi, Arusha, Thaara, Sagana or Embu. == References == Category:Populated places in Central Province (Kenya)
title: Kangenga
